We have several 16Amp caravan plug sites available for your EV, irrespective of whether you are staying in one of our tent, cabins, tourist flats, studio units or motel units. You can take a bush walk around Ross Creek Reservour (just alongside our park)while you recharge, or 2-3 hour walk up The "Pineapple Track" to the hills overlooking Dunedin; or go and see the local glow worms if you are staying overnight.
